#Keyboard
W,S,A,D     Move
TAB         Display score

#Mouse
LMB         Shoot

#Debug mode
]           Toggle debug node visibility ON/OFF

#The debug functionalities below will still work even when debug node visibility is turned off. 
/           Highlight node
M           Connect two nodes
.           Add new node (connected to the previous node)
SHIFT + .   Add new node (disconnected)

Up-arrow    Change node type to normal
Down-arrow  Change node type to camp (Bot Behavior not implemented!!)
Left-arrow  Change node type to spawn-point
Right-arrow Change node type to goal-roam
